<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><img src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C00000038j57&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1460743550000" alt="Right click on the image to save it to your computer."></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">{!Contact.FirstName}, if you're free this Sunday then Tesco need </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">you</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">!</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Tesco and All Active Brent are running a brilliant pre-Race for Life bootcamp <b>this Sunday</b>&nbsp;and they'd love volunteers who've completed NCS in Barnet. That means you're invited!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b>Skills you will need:</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial">Enthusiasm</font></li><li><font face="arial">Initiative</font></li><li><font face="arial">Interest in helping others keep fit</font></li></ul><div><font face="arial"><b>Details for the day:</b></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial">10am to 4pm at <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Willesden+Sports+Centre/@51.5402178,-0.2332427,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x4876104b9090b8c7:0x9cbde493974dcc9e">Willesden Sports Centre</a></font></li><li>You'll be helping to run a bootcamp for women and children who are interested in running Cancer Research's Race for Life</li><li>Lots of different opportunities available - from running the registration desk to supporting with the bootcamp sessions, there's something for everyone!</li></ul><div><b>How to get involved:</b></div></div><div><ul><li><span style="font-family: arial;">Send a text to Tesco's volunteer co-ordinator&nbsp;<b>Marcie Thomas</b><b>&nbsp;</b>on&nbsp;<b>07944829508</b></span></li><li><font face="arial">State your name and what <b>times you are free</b> to volunteer</font></li><li><font face="arial">Wait for her to call you back to confirm!</font></li></ul><span style="font-family: arial;">This opportunity is&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: arial;">not</b><span style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;organised by The Challenge Society - you'll be a volunteer with Tesco and All Active Brent. Please do not respond to this email to organise your volunteering, as we are not involved in the day.</span></div><div><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Have a great weekend!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards,</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Challenge Society</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" color="#666666"><b><a href="http://tcsnorthlondon.co.uk/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">www.tcsnorthlondon.co.uk</a></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div>]]></td>
